{"tid":2067599,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"斷腳都入選港隊","createTime":"2020-06-17T06:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T06:18:05.000Z","uid":11081,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"846ec7165bbf492ecb52eded0c2ad034be3691da","tid":2067599,"uid":11081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T06:05:07.000Z","msg":"2018年亞運泳隊選拔爭議不絕，民主黨立法會議員林卓廷指，現已退役的港將王俊仁於亞運前三個多月小腿骨折，竟獲選代表港隊出戰50米蛙泳，質疑港協所謂考慮運動員賽前六個月備賽計劃的準則名存實亡。港協行政總監鄭國鴻解釋，體院總教練當時未有通報其傷患，及至上次聆訊始知悉事件，林卓廷表示震驚，「運動員傷到膝頭要開刀，小腿骨要打釘，行路都有困難，起碼都要兩個月埋骨，慢慢再要物理治療，難以理解港協同泳總完全唔知」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200617/GIDFE3JBP6ELDHNDPDM3663IRA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200617%2FGIDFE3JBP6ELDHNDPDM3663IRA%2F&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG2%2FWCCUevL1oElw8znUqpaw%3D&h=0b890be1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200617%2FGIDFE3JBP6ELDHNDPDM3663IRA%2F&h=7576cbe9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200617/GIDFE3JBP6ELDHNDPDM3663IRA/</a><br />\n<br />\n唔講以為係殘奧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f3a184e1d26627f67cd8f44fd4c200aace8cdf","tid":2067599,"uid":203058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T06:18:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />陳柒踢唔到咪照選佢去日本shopping"}]}